Program: Crossing Continents
Title: The Congo Connection
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00nvz74
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 23 Nov 2009
Peter Greste investigates whether Rwandans in France and Germany are controlling a deadly African militia. For the last 15 years, the rebels of the FDLR have enforced their control through a series of brutal atrocities. Now Crossing Continents has secret intelligence suggesting that they were taking orders from political leaders living openly in Europe. Show less